<body>
    <h1>Re-Hire (Associate) (Use Case =E2=80=93 UC10)</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h3 id=3D"Re-Hire(Associate)(UseCase=E2=80=93UC10)-Re-Hireworkflow"=
>Re-Hire workflow</h3>
<p>Table-25</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"a=
6d1068d-34e7-4bb8-a82a-dbce59473f0f" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<colgroup>
<col style=3D"width: 317.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 1482.0px;">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Type</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Re-Hire</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Description</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>The Re-Hire use case describes the reintegration of former associate in =
Ascension Health Alliance systems via SailPoint IdentityIQ. SailPoint Ident=
ityIQ will automatically reinstate access privileges for rehired users base=
d on their current role. Associated downstream systems accounts will be re-=
enabled.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>List of Attributes&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>The following set of attributes represent the tentative set of users=E2=
=80=99 attributes which will be used in the process flow. The final set of =
source and target attributes will be finalized in the solution design docum=
ent.</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>First Name</p></li>
<li>
<p>Last Name&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Person Number&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Assignment Status</p></li>
<li>
<p>System Worker Type</p></li>
<li>
<p>Action Name</p></li>
<li>
<p>Start Date</p></li>
<li>
<p>Hire Date</p></li>
<li>
<p>Effective Date</p></li>
<li>
<p>Department</p></li>
<li>
<p>Position</p></li>
<li>
<p>Location</p></li>
<li>
<p>Ministry</p></li>
<li>
<p>Workrelationship Primary Flag</p></li>
</ol>
<p></p>
<p>Refer Appendix =E2=80=9C<a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://drive=
.google.com/drive/folders/17u4oN4VdyLijziIcn8PMSlUxT5HS_LW0" rel=3D"nofollo=
w"><u>Source and Target Attribute Mapping</u></a>=E2=80=9D for complete lis=
t of attribute mapping.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Pre-Conditions</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Rehire account will match with the existing user personal ID.&nbsp;User =
identity object and its past access should already be present in SailPoint =
IdentityIQ in terminated state.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Trigger</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>When following conditions are true:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>The Hire Date should match with the current date.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Associate ID should match with existing Associate ID in SailPoint Identi=
tyIQ with Termination state, Re-Hire account will match with the existing u=
ser personal ID.</p></li>
<li>
<p>=E2=80=98<strong>System Worker Type</strong>=E2=80=99 attribute should b=
e updated from =E2=80=98<strong>Pending Worker</strong>=E2=80=99 to =E2=80=
=98<strong>Associate</strong>=E2=80=99.</p></li>
<li>
<p>=E2=80=98<strong>Assignment status</strong>=E2=80=99 attribute should be=
 equal to =E2=80=98<strong>Active - Payroll Eligible</strong>=E2=80=99.</p>=
</li>
<li>
<p>=E2=80=98<strong>Action Name</strong>=E2=80=99 attributes value should e=
qual to =E2=80=98<strong>Rehire</strong>=E2=80=99.</p></li>
</ol></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Basic Flow</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Enable existing user identity in SailPoint IdentityIQ.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Enable the downstream application accounts, if they exist, or provision =
new accounts based on birthright access roles.</p></li>
<li>
<p>SailPoint IdentityIQ will provision SSO identifier&nbsp;(UPN - <a class=
=3D"external-link" href=3D"mailto:fname.lname@ascension.org" rel=3D"nofollo=
w"><u>fname.lname@ascension.org</u></a>) to Oracle HR system.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Reset users Active Directory account=E2=80=99s password and share the pa=
ssword via email to user and the NAN leadership mailbox team will be notifi=
ed via email by following Ascension Health Alliance=E2=80=99s email securit=
y policies.</p></li>
</ol></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>List of downstream applications</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Active Directory, Azure, GSuite, ServiceNow, Oracle ERP Cloud, Oracle EP=
M Cloud, OCI.&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Acceptance criteria</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Enable SailPoint IdentityIQ Identity downstream application accounts, if=
 they exist, or provision new accounts based on birthright access roles.</p=
>
<p>Provision SSO identifier&nbsp;(UPN - <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"=
mailto:fname.lname@ascension.org" rel=3D"nofollow">fname.lname@ascension.or=
g</a>) to Oracle HR system.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Error handling</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>A ServiceNow ticket will be created and assigned to the Ascension Health=
 Alliance SailPoint IIQ support team.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Persona / Actors</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Automated Process</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p></p>
<p><strong>Dependency:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"959" data-layout=3D"center" data-local-id=3D"d67=
d52a7-b39c-42c6-af82-4430de7e1722" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<colgroup>
<col style=3D"width: 61.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 176.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 722.0px;">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d4deec" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>S. no</p></td>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d4deec" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Dependency</p></td>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d4deec" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Point of contact for answers</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>1</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>List of attributes</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Oracle HCM Cloud application team to send the final set of attributes ma=
pping</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>2</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Trigger</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Oracle HCM Cloud application team to finalize the attributes and its val=
ues required for trigger</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Acceptance criteria</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Ascension Health Alliance team to confirm the list of birthright access =
applications based on demographic data</p>
<p>Oracle HCM Cloud application team to provide users=E2=80=99 demographic =
information and access mapping for Re-Hire:</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
